.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, davidoff, bolivar
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, soccer
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, train
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the bolivar-smoker is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage    | coffee    | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| Cigar       | davidoff   | bolivar  | vegafina  |
| Sport         | volleyball      | skiing     | soccer    |
| Transport   | motorbike | train    | ship        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, video-games
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, cape-cod
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
There 3 different types of food: peach, onion, garlic
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating onion is between the person eating peach and the cape-cod house##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating onion##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Hobby         | video-games | board-games | drawing |
| House           | cape-cod     | farmhouse    | gothic-revival |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Food           | garlic         | onion      | peach    |

