.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, sailing, rugby
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish, ferret
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, nigerian
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is rugby is between the nigerian and the person who's sport is tennis##2
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | cola       | sprite   |
| Sport          | tennis   | rugby   | sailing     |
| Pet         | fish  | goldfish    | ferret  |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian | nigerian |

