.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, blend
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pepper, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, indie
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, swimming, baseball
1. the person who's sport is swimming is between the montecristo-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the fan of classical##1
5. the blend-smoker is between the person eating pepper and the person eating radish##2
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the fan of indie##1
8. the person eating pepper is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Cigar      | ritmeester   | blend    | montecristo   |
| Food          | radish | eggplant  | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | classical | indie  |
| Sport     | rugby | swimming   | baseball  |

