.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, chef, videographer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain, bolivar
City: edinburgh, prague, berlin
1. the person eating asparagus is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
3. the videographer is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the cain-smoker##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is between the person traveling to berlin and the chef##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| Job           | chef      | analyst  | videographer |
| Cigar   | cain  | aristoff   | bolivar  |
| City           | edinburgh      | prague | berlin        |

