.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, mauve, red
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, bus
3 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, rugby, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
8. the owner of the cat is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Color   | apricot         | red      | mauve   |
| Transport        | bus | train          | quad-bike |
| Pet        | cat         | lizard        | pony       |
| Sport      | rugby       | skateboarding | golf       |

