The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, trike
1. the person eating pumpkin is the person driving the bus##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the bongani-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Cigar       | bongani | prince    | blend |
| Food         | raspberry   | tomato | pumpkin     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig  | mouse     | frog        |
| Transport   | trike       | jet-ski   | bus         |

