There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory, green
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, soul
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, june, january
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes green is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person who likes ivory##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk       | coffee | almond-milk |
| Color          | ivory  | chestnut | green   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | soul   | folk        |
| Birthday     | january | june    | august        |

