.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, chess, video-games
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, zinnia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, russian, thai
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the russian is the russian##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is between the argentine and the russian##2
7. the fan of d&b is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby      | video-games     | chess | hiking  |
| Flower          | zinnia   | sunflower     | lily  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | blues    | classical |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai     | russian   |

