.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, reading
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, documentary, martial-arts
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person drinking milk is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person drinking water##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | reading   | photography | fishing  |
| Beverage         | juice      | milk      | water   |
| Movie-Genre       | documentary      | martial-arts       | sports |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike       | tram     |

