.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, pineapple, watermelon
City: marseilles, colone, paris
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, sports
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, milk
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to colone##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | nectarine | pineapple |
| City           | marseilles   | paris   | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | drama     | disaster  |
| Beverage   | cola     | milk  | almond-milk   |

