.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, tomato
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, turquise, pink
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dannemann, pall-mall
1. the person eating tomato is between the person eating apple and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating tomato is between the dannemann-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
5. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
7. the person who likes pink is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| Food       | kiwi          | tomato     | apple       |
| Color      | pink       | turquise | apricot |
| Cigar        | dannemann          | pall-mall       | bluemaster        |

