.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, reading, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, water-polo
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, soy-milk
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | reading      | sudoku     | collecting |
| Sport           | rowing | snowboarding | water-polo     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | fanta       | soy-milk      |
| Pet           | cat          | frog       | rabbit     |

