3 different pets are kept: dog, fish, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, snowboarding
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, firefighter, designer
1. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the firefighter is on the left or right of the designer##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is between the owner of the fish and the palace house##2
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
5. the palace house is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
7. the palace house is the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| House        | palace       | gothic-revival     | farmhouse   |
| Pet         | dog          | lizard    | fish       |
| Sport       | snowboarding | badminton | ice-hockey |
| Job   | dressmaker          | designer       | firefighter |

