.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, pop, gospel
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, jet-ski
3 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, turtle
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
7. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre           | disco  | gospel  | pop      |
| Transport   | jet-ski | taxi | airplane     |
| Pet           | turtle  | ferret | horse         |

 